    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1938-04-25T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1938-04-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="917"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d917">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">562.8F3/17</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Norwegian Minister</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morgenstierne</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-04-25">April 25,
                            1938</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Acting under instructions from my Government I
                    have the honor to inform you that it has been decided to call an informal
                    preliminary conference of experts in Oslo beginning on May 19th next in
                    preparation for the Whaling Conference to be held in London in June this
                    year.</p>
                <p>My Government has requested me to convey to the Government of the United States
                    an invitation to take part in such a preliminary conference and to express the
                    hope that in the event of the invitation <pb facs="0956" n="948" xml:id="pg_948"
                    /> being accepted the American representatives to the conference may find it
                    possible to be present in Oslo on the date mentioned.</p>
                <p>I have further been instructed to inform you that in the opinion of the Norwegian
                    Government it would be desirable that no reference be made in the Press to the
                    said preliminary conference in Oslo.</p>
                <p>Accept [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>W. <hi rend="smallcaps">Morgenstierne</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
